{"source": "zhihu", "record_type": "question", "item_id": "2050951363807405043", "url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2050951363807405043", "title": "如何评价追光动画出品的电影《三国第一部：争洛阳》？", "body": "", "author_name": "", "author_id": "", "images": [], "videos": [], "cover_url": "", "metrics": {"views": 0, "likes": 0, "comments": 0, "shares": 0, "favorites": 0}, "html_snapshot": "", "api_response": {"id": 2050951363807405043, "title": "如何评价追光动画出品的电影《三国第一部：争洛阳》？", "url": "https://api.zhihu.com/questions/2050951363807405043", "type": "question", "created": 1781764909, "answer_count": 172, "follower_count": 247, "author": {"type": "people", "user_type": "people", "id": "0", "url_token": "", "url": "", "name": "用户", "headline": "", "avatar_url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"}, "bound_topic_ids": [68, 3676, 15840, 3590673, 4496224], "comment_count": 0, "is_following": false, "excerpt": "东汉末年，三国鼎立大幕未启，黄巾军起，外戚弄权，宦官乱政。天下动荡之际，曹操、袁绍欲借大将军何进之力制衡宦官，匡扶汉室。不料董卓趁乱进京，图谋废立。乱世棋局渐开，袁术、吕布、孙坚及刘关张等各路群雄相继登场，洛阳风云起，大汉的命运走向十字路口。"}, "extra": {"metrics_text": ""}, "comments": [], "scraped_at": "2026-07-11T05:04:36.251622"}
